# .gitignore for goscape-client.

# === Compiled binaries ===
# Anchored with a leading slash so ONLY root-level binaries match — the
# `cmd/client/` SOURCE directory must NOT be ignored.
/client
/bin/
*.exe

# === Test / coverage / profiling output ===
*.test
coverage.txt
coverage.html
test_results.txt
*.prof
*.pprof
*.pb.gz
# SIGUSR1 pprof captures written by pkg/profiling.
/profiles/

# === Local / private config — never push ===
# CLAUDE.local.md is private per its own header (CLAUDE.md, by contrast, is
# meant to be committed — do not add it here).
CLAUDE.local.md
# Claude Code: per-user local settings + personal session state. To SHARE
# team config, un-ignore specific paths, e.g.:
#   !.claude/settings.json
#   !.claude/commands/
.claude/
# Project MCP config can carry server URLs / tokens — ignore by default.
.mcp.json

# === Editors / IDEs ===
.idea/
.vscode/
*.swp
*~

# === Tool caches ===
.serena/

# === OS cruft ===
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
